{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":465,"text":"In Kenya, 1984 is known"},{"time":3722,"text":"as the year of the cup,"},{"time":6333,"text":"or the goro goro."},{"time":8753,"text":"The goro goro is a cup used to measure"},{"time":11671,"text":"two kilograms of maize flower on the market,"},{"time":14981,"text":"and the maize flower is used to make ugali,"},{"time":18121,"text":"a polenta-like cake that is eaten\ntogether with vegetables."},{"time":22078,"text":"Both the maize and the vegetables are grown"},{"time":24393,"text":"on most Kenyan farms,"},{"time":26518,"text":"which means that most families can feed themselves"},{"time":28791,"text":"from their own farm."},{"time":30972,"text":"One goro goro can feed three meals"},{"time":34900,"text":"for an average family,"},{"time":36881,"text":"and in 1984, the whole harvest"},{"time":39970,"text":"could fit in one goro goro."},{"time":43142,"text":"It was and still is one of the worst droughts"},{"time":45992,"text":"in living memory."},{"time":48635,"text":"Now today, I insure farmers against droughts"},{"time":51594,"text":"like those in the year of the cup,"},{"time":53655,"text":"or to be more specific, I insure the rains."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58641,"text":"I come from a family of missionaries"},{"time":61090,"text":"who built hospitals in Indonesia,"},{"time":63241,"text":"and my father built a psychiatric hospital"},{"time":65518,"text":"in Tanzania."},{"time":66774,"text":"This is me, age five, in front of that hospital."},{"time":69875,"text":"I don't think they thought I'd grow up"},{"time":72196,"text":"to sell insurance. (Laughter)"},{"time":75162,"text":"So let me tell you how that happened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78203,"text":"In 2008, I was working"},{"time":79920,"text":"for the Ministry of Agriculture of Rwanda,"},{"time":82204,"text":"and my boss had just been promoted"},{"time":84200,"text":"to become the minister."},{"time":85607,"text":"She launched an ambitious plan"},{"time":87495,"text":"to start a green revolution in her country,"},{"time":89824,"text":"and before we knew it, we were importing"},{"time":91444,"text":"tons of fertilizer and seed"},{"time":93737,"text":"and telling farmers how to apply that fertilizer"},{"time":96462,"text":"and plant."},{"time":97997,"text":"A couple of weeks later,"},{"time":99890,"text":"the International Monetary Fund visited us,"},{"time":102603,"text":"and asked my minister,"},{"time":104133,"text":"\"Minister, it's great that you want to help farmers"},{"time":106945,"text":"reach food security, but what if it doesn't rain?\""},{"time":111118,"text":"My minister answered proudly"},{"time":113267,"text":"and somewhat defiantly,"},{"time":115281,"text":"\"I am going to pray for rain.\""},{"time":119871,"text":"That ended the discussion."},{"time":123071,"text":"On the way back to the ministry in the car,"},{"time":125225,"text":"she turned around to me and said,"},{"time":127306,"text":"\"Rose, you've always been interested in finance."},{"time":129376,"text":"Go find us some insurance.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":132515,"text":"It's been six years since,"},{"time":134552,"text":"and last year I was fortunate enough"},{"time":136542,"text":"to be part of a team that insured"},{"time":138048,"text":"over 185,000 farmers in Kenya and Rwanda"},{"time":141953,"text":"against drought."},{"time":143890,"text":"They owned an average of half an acre"},{"time":145970,"text":"and paid on average two Euros in premium."},{"time":149423,"text":"It's microinsurance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151800,"text":"Now, traditional insurance doesn't work"},{"time":153855,"text":"with two to three Euros of premium,"},{"time":155768,"text":"because traditional insurance relies on farm visits."},{"time":158675,"text":"A farmer here in Germany would be visited"},{"time":160617,"text":"for the start of the season, halfway through,"},{"time":163102,"text":"and at the end, and again if there was a loss,"},{"time":165589,"text":"to estimate the damages."},{"time":168995,"text":"For a small-scale farmer in the middle of Africa,"},{"time":172130,"text":"the maths of doing those visits"},{"time":173959,"text":"simply don't add up."},{"time":177030,"text":"So instead, we rely on technology and data."},{"time":180871,"text":"This satellite measures"},{"time":183077,"text":"whether there were clouds or not,"},{"time":185239,"text":"because think about it:"},{"time":186407,"text":"If there are clouds, then you might have some rain,"},{"time":191109,"text":"but if there are no clouds,"},{"time":192808,"text":"then it's actually impossible for it to rain."},{"time":195659,"text":"These images show the onset of the rains"},{"time":197939,"text":"this season in Kenya."},{"time":199794,"text":"You see that around March 6,"},{"time":201830,"text":"the clouds move in and then disappear,"},{"time":204935,"text":"and then around the March 11,"},{"time":206963,"text":"the clouds really move in."},{"time":210213,"text":"That, and those clouds,"},{"time":213140,"text":"were the onset of the rains this year."},{"time":216028,"text":"This satellite covers the whole of Africa"},{"time":218715,"text":"and goes back as far as 1984,"},{"time":221632,"text":"and that's important, because if you know"},{"time":223980,"text":"how many times a place has had a drought"},{"time":226421,"text":"in the last 30 years,"},{"time":228370,"text":"you can make a pretty good estimate"},{"time":230200,"text":"what the chances are of drought in the future,"},{"time":232957,"text":"and that means that you can put a price tag"},{"time":235070,"text":"on the risk of drought."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237760,"text":"The data alone isn't enough."},{"time":240156,"text":"We devise agronomic algorithms"},{"time":242641,"text":"which tell us how much rainfall\na crop needs and when."},{"time":246335,"text":"For example, for maize at planting,"},{"time":248749,"text":"you need to have two days of rain"},{"time":251144,"text":"for farmers to plant,"},{"time":253000,"text":"and then it needs to rain once every two weeks"},{"time":255194,"text":"for the crop to properly germinate."},{"time":257673,"text":"After that, you need rain every three weeks"},{"time":260998,"text":"for the crop to form its leaves,"},{"time":263901,"text":"whereas at flowering, you\nneed it to rain more frequently,"},{"time":266667,"text":"about once every 10 days\nfor the crop to form its cob."},{"time":270527,"text":"At the end of the season,"},{"time":272032,"text":"you actually don't want it to rain,"},{"time":274244,"text":"because rains then can damage the crop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277795,"text":"Devising such a cover is difficult,"},{"time":281150,"text":"but it turned out the real challenge"},{"time":283046,"text":"was selling insurance."},{"time":287574,"text":"We set ourselves a modest target"},{"time":290061,"text":"of 500 farmers insured after our first season."},{"time":294061,"text":"After a couple of months' intense marketing,"},{"time":296631,"text":"we had signed up the grand total"},{"time":298450,"text":"of 185 farmers."},{"time":302108,"text":"I was disappointed and confounded."},{"time":305030,"text":"Everybody kept telling me that farmers"},{"time":306684,"text":"wanted insurance,"},{"time":309267,"text":"but our prime customers simply weren't buying."},{"time":312264,"text":"They were waiting to see what would happen,"},{"time":314928,"text":"didn't trust insurance companies,"},{"time":317677,"text":"or thought, \"I've managed for so many years."},{"time":319963,"text":"Why would I buy insurance now?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":323720,"text":"Now many of you know microcredit,"},{"time":326102,"text":"the method of providing small loans to poor people"},{"time":329596,"text":"pioneered by Muhammad Yunus,"},{"time":331598,"text":"who won the Nobel Peace Prize"},{"time":333119,"text":"for his work with the Grameen Bank."},{"time":335268,"text":"Turns out, selling microcredit"},{"time":337752,"text":"isn't the same as selling insurance."},{"time":341153,"text":"For credit, a farmer needs\nto earn the trust of a bank,"},{"time":345038,"text":"and if it succeeds, the bank will advance him money."},{"time":348982,"text":"That's an attractive proposition."},{"time":351091,"text":"For insurance, the farmer needs to trust"},{"time":354337,"text":"the insurance company, and needs"},{"time":355879,"text":"to advance the insurance company money."},{"time":359103,"text":"It's a very different value proposition."},{"time":362470,"text":"And so the uptick of insurance has been slow,"},{"time":365159,"text":"with so far only 4.4 percent of Africans"},{"time":367735,"text":"taking up insurance in 2012,"},{"time":370288,"text":"and half of that number is in one country,"},{"time":372280,"text":"South Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374323,"text":"We tried for some years"},{"time":375970,"text":"selling insurance directly to farmers,"},{"time":378421,"text":"with very high marketing cost"},{"time":380420,"text":"and very limited success."},{"time":383506,"text":"Then we realized that there were many organizations"},{"time":385460,"text":"working with farmers:"},{"time":388169,"text":"seed companies, microfinance institutions,"},{"time":391606,"text":"mobile phone companies,"},{"time":393552,"text":"government agencies."},{"time":394874,"text":"They were all providing loans to farmers,"},{"time":397624,"text":"and often, just before they'd finalize the loan,"},{"time":400246,"text":"the farmer would say,"},{"time":402346,"text":"\"But what if it doesn't rain?"},{"time":404498,"text":"How do you expect me to repay my loan?\""},{"time":407965,"text":"Many of these organizations"},{"time":410042,"text":"were taking on the risk themselves,"},{"time":411660,"text":"simply hoping that that year,"},{"time":413628,"text":"the worst wouldn't happen."},{"time":415990,"text":"Most of the organizations, however,"},{"time":417996,"text":"were limiting their growth in agriculture."},{"time":420319,"text":"They couldn't take on this kind of risk."},{"time":422991,"text":"These organizations became our customers,"},{"time":426714,"text":"and when combining credit and insurance,"},{"time":429913,"text":"interesting things can happen."},{"time":432632,"text":"Let me tell you one more story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436020,"text":"At the start of February 2012 in western Kenya,"},{"time":439870,"text":"the rains started, and they started early,"},{"time":442869,"text":"and when rains start early, farmers are encouraged,"},{"time":445940,"text":"because it usually means that\nthe season is going to be good."},{"time":449506,"text":"So they took out loans and planted."},{"time":452262,"text":"For the next three weeks,"},{"time":453752,"text":"there wasn't a single drop of rain,"},{"time":456060,"text":"and the crops that had germinated so well"},{"time":458624,"text":"shriveled and died."},{"time":461937,"text":"We'd insured the loans of a microfinance institution"},{"time":464692,"text":"that had provided those loans"},{"time":465812,"text":"to about 6,000 farmers in that area,"},{"time":469360,"text":"and we called them up and said,"},{"time":470650,"text":"\"Look, we know about the drought."},{"time":472350,"text":"We've got you."},{"time":474014,"text":"We'll give you 200,000 Euros\nat the end of the season.\""},{"time":478327,"text":"They said, \"Wow, that's great,"},{"time":480126,"text":"but that'll be late."},{"time":482252,"text":"Could you give us the money now?"},{"time":484435,"text":"Then these farmers can still replant"},{"time":486865,"text":"and can get a harvest this season.\""},{"time":490442,"text":"So we convinced our insurance partners,"},{"time":492523,"text":"and later that April, these farmers replanted."},{"time":495898,"text":"We took the idea of replanting to a seed company"},{"time":498692,"text":"and convinced them to price the cost of insurance"},{"time":500802,"text":"into every bag of seed,"},{"time":502941,"text":"and in every bag, we packed a card"},{"time":504920,"text":"that had a number on it,"},{"time":506494,"text":"and when the farmers would open the card,"},{"time":508476,"text":"they'd text in that number,"},{"time":510477,"text":"and that number would actually help us"},{"time":511850,"text":"to locate the farmer"},{"time":513225,"text":"and allocate them to a satellite pixel."},{"time":516349,"text":"A satellite would then measure the rainfall"},{"time":518891,"text":"for the next three weeks,"},{"time":520424,"text":"and if it didn't rain,"},{"time":522154,"text":"we'd replace their seed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525560,"text":"One of the first —"},{"time":526800,"text":"(Applause) — Hold on, I'm not there!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":532023,"text":"One of the first beneficiaries\nof this replanting guarantee"},{"time":535180,"text":"was Bosco Mwinyi."},{"time":537396,"text":"We visited his farm later that August,"},{"time":540087,"text":"and I wish I could show you the smile on his face"},{"time":543643,"text":"when he showed us his harvest,"},{"time":546107,"text":"because it warmed my heart"},{"time":547740,"text":"and it made me realize why selling insurance"},{"time":549678,"text":"can be a good thing."},{"time":552388,"text":"But you know, he insisted"},{"time":553936,"text":"that we get his whole harvest in the picture,"},{"time":556890,"text":"so we had to zoom out a lot."},{"time":560753,"text":"Insurance secured his harvest that season,"},{"time":563982,"text":"and I believe that today,"},{"time":566502,"text":"we have all the tools to enable African farmers"},{"time":569685,"text":"to take control of their own destiny."},{"time":572452,"text":"No more years of the cup."},{"time":573951,"text":"Instead, I am looking forward to, at least somehow,"},{"time":577289,"text":"the year of the insurance,"},{"time":579945,"text":"or the year of the great harvest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582648,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":585850,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}